OL,3,CSummer in Svalbard: Ice scientists
OL,4,Cfighting against warmest season on
OL,5,Crecord
OL,7,FClimate research scientists are
OL,8,Finvestigating how changes to
OL,9,Ftemperatures are impacting the local
OL,10,Fwildlife
OL,12,FGlaciers have shaped the arctic
OL,13,Farchipelago of Svalbard for millennia.
OL,15,FThe islands have just had their
OL,16,Fwarmest summer on modern record -
OL,17,Ftemperatures 3C above the average.
OL,19,FThis is evidence that our climate is
OL,20,Fnearing a tipping point.
