OL,3,CSummer in Svalbard: Ice scientists
OL,4,Cfighting against warmest season on
OL,5,Crecord
OL,7,FIce scientist Dorothea Moser is taking
OL,8,Fme from the British arctic station to
OL,9,Fthe rapidly retreating Broggerbreane
OL,10,Fglacier.
OL,12,FAs we walk past treeless slopes
OL,13,Fcontorted by tectonic movement,
OL,14,FDorothea shows me how the ice has
OL,15,Fshaped the geology over millions of
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
