OL,3,CSummer in Svalbard: Ice scientists
OL,4,Cfighting against warmest season on
OL,5,Crecord
OL,7,FGlaciers have grown and shrunk so
OL,8,Fwhat's to make us think current
OL,9,Fchanges aren't just natural
OL,10,Ffluctuations? Her answer is short and
OL,11,Fclear.
OL,13,F"It's all to do with the speed and the
OL,14,Fscale."
