OL,3,CSummer in Svalbard: Ice scientists
OL,4,Cfighting against warmest season on
OL,5,Crecord
OL,7,FWe can see the glacier's life ebbing
OL,8,Faway. Snaking streams of iron-rich red
OL,9,Fmeltwater leaching into the fjord.
OL,11,FWe see a pod of beluga whales
OL,12,Fapparently enjoying the nutrient-rich
OL,13,Fwater. Their numbers have stabilised
OL,14,Fsince hunting was capped.
OL,16,FOn land things are changing too. For
OL,17,F10 years, British Antarctic Scientist
OL,18,FKevin Newsham has been studying the
OL,19,Fgreenification of the Arctic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
