OL,4,Cfighting against warmest season on
OL,5,Crecord
OL,7,FMini glass houses warm soil by a
OL,8,Fdegree to see what vegetation will
OL,9,Fgrow in the future.
OL,11,FIn the lab, he's trying to understand
OL,12,Fwhether the amount of carbon collected
OL,13,Fby photosynthesis will offset the
OL,14,Famount released by microbes in the
OL,15,Fthawing soil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
